							after.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="py-3">
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
							<strong class="text-white">Power Night Mode</strong> - At 11 PM, Home Assistant SSHs into
							<a
								href="https://www.proxmox.com/en/proxmox-virtual-environment"
								target="_blank"
								rel="noopener noreferrer"
								class="text-coral hover:text-teal">Proxmox</a
							> and shuts down non-essential containers, saving ~175W overnight. At 7 AM, everything restarts
							and health checks confirm services are back before reporting success. Manual override available
							for late nights.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p class="text-xs font-mono text-teal mb-3 mt-6">context-aware routines</p>
				<div class="divide-y divide-surface-3/50">
					<div class="py-3">
