							<strong class="text-white">Weather-aware mornings</strong> - "Good Morning" checks the forecast:
							opens curtains if mild, closes blackout curtains if &gt;85&deg;F and high UV. Chooses between
							natural light and warm scene based on whether the sun is up yet.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="py-3">
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
							<strong class="text-white">Vacation presence simulation</strong> - Activates realistic light
							patterns that mimic normal activity, arms alarm in vacation mode, returns vacuums to base,
							closes all blinds, adjusts climate to away preset. Reverses everything on return.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="py-3">
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-400">
